# Gauge.StandardModel

SU(3) × SU(2) × U(1) gauge structure.

The Standard Model gauge group is G_SM = SU(3)_c × SU(2)_L × U(1)_Y (up to
a finite quotient). Its Lie algebra is:
  𝔤_SM = su(3) ⊕ su(2) ⊕ u(1)  ≅  A₂ ⊕ A₁ ⊕ ℝ

This module defines the combined gauge algebra and assembles the individual
factors from `PhysicsSM.Gauge.SU3`, `PhysicsSM.Gauge.SU2`, `PhysicsSM.Gauge.U1`.

Prerequisites:
- `PhysicsSM.Gauge.U1`
- `PhysicsSM.Gauge.SU2`
- `PhysicsSM.Gauge.SU3`

Status: stub.
-/

